msgctxt "56_Chase Battles (Pursuing)"
msgid ""
"When you are the pursuer in a chase event, capture the enemy by depleting "
"their Chase Gauge to almost zero and tackling with "
"<Action:Button_Square@Chase>. You can also deliver the finishing blow by "
"picking up an object during the chase and pressing "
"<Action:Button_Circle@Chase> to throw it at the enemy."
msgstr ""
"Quando insegui durante un inseguimento, cattura il nemico azzerando quasi "
"del tutto il suo indicatore inseguimento e placcandolo con "
"<Action:Button_Square@Chase>. Puoi anche assestare il colpo di grazia "
"raccogliendo un oggetto durante l'inseguimento e premendo "
"<Action:Button_Circle@Chase> per lanciarlo contro il nemico."

msgctxt "68_Chase Battles (Pursuing)"
msgid ""
"Deliver precise tackles by wisely navigating your way through the course or "
"dashing with "
"<Action:Button_LS_Up@Chase><Action:Button_LS_Down@Chase><Action:Button_LS_Left@Chase><Action:Button_LS_Right@Chase>."
msgstr ""
"Esegui placcaggi precisi muovendoti saggiamente lungo il percorso o "
"scattando con "
"<Action:Button_LS_Up@Chase><Action:Button_LS_Down@Chase><Action:Button_LS_Left@Chase><Action:Button_LS_Right@Chase>."

